    "It is designed to perform general-purpose tasks and can be fine-tuned for domain-specific tasks.",
    "The fine-tuning process was performed on a single Tesla T4 GPU with 16 gigabytes of GPU VRAM.",
    "Due to hardware constraints, we employed a QLoRA method.",
    "This method involved reducing the precision of model parameters to 4-bit integers, significantly reducing the amount of CPU and GPU memory required, making it feasible to perform the experiment on the available hardware.",
    "The dataset used for fine-tuning was self-generated and consisted of headlines and their respective news articles."
